# Brand Guidelines

> **Reference this document when building UI components, choosing colors, writing copy, or making design decisions.** Keep tokens in sync across web/mobile. Follow accessibility rules by default (WCAG AA, AAA where feasible).

> See also: [coding.mdc](./coding.mdc) for implementation details.

